author: J14T14
title: 1677-1 Rabbit Rehash
review:
I was searching through the SEASONAL theme on this website when I discovered this set. I realized that it was completely identical to 1677-1 Rabbit. Never the less, this set still looks good. The print is detailed enough for the time and the 1x1 round studs work great as buck teeth. The rabbit seems to be wearing blue pants, a red shirt, and a red hat. It is cartoony, but fun as a small toy for kids.

Overall I like this set, though it is not the best. This can be chalked up to it being an older model that was released 13 years after it was originally designed, but this also makes it kind of charming. It is nothing to spend a lot of money to get new, but it is still nice to have.
